---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>

<section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">

  <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
    Tips Before Travelling Australia
  </h1>

  <img
    src="/images/blogs/australia.jpg"
    alt="Australia"
    class="rounded-3xl w-full h-[400px] object-cover mb-10"
  />

  <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700 mb-6">
    Australia is huge and diverse. Here are 10 essential tips before you go…
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4">
    1. Plan your route
  </h2>

  <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
    Distances in Australia are massive, so don’t underestimate travel time…
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4">
    2. Budget properly
  </h2>

  <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
    Australia is not cheap. Expect higher costs for food and accommodation…
  </p>

</section>

</BaseLayout>